{
  "stem": "1568.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Actually, I really don't recall, and most likely we went by train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I am not specific, but we went by train, most likely.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, again, in Blizyn you lived already in barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had a barrack and you had bunkers and you slept one alongside the other, like sardines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As I say, you-- you would get up in the morning and go to work and then you had [SIGHS] a count, you know, to see that everybody was there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were surrounded by barbed wires with towers under.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The police were still the Jewish police from Tomaszow were still like the kapo, and they're taking care of the-- of the daily supposedly.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They watched that you stayed in line to get your food and the necessities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We did not have the-- the German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The only German was-- is in the factory, where he watched us work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How were the conditions?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother got sick of typhus in-- in-- in Blizyn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father died in Blizyn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- as far as I know, he died of natural causes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was it malnutrition?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did he give us the food?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was it broken heart?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was it a heart attack?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They buried him-- it was surrounded by forest, the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They buried him in the forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had the privilege to go out and bury him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But until now, 52, 53 years, I couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I became hysterical and whoever tried to convince me, I just didn't go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My brother went, but [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I did not come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[SIGHS] That was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] basically life in Blizyn.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
